made pursuant to the safe harbor provisions of the Private Securities Litigation Reform Act of 1995. Forward-<br>
looking statements involve known and unknown risks and uncertainties that may cause the actual results in future<br>
periods of Aegean Marine Petroleum Network, Inc. to differ materially from forecasted results. Those risks<br>
include, among others, changes in customer orders and demand for our products; the liquidity of credit markets;<br>
changes in raw material, labor, equipment and transportation costs; pricing actions by the Company and its<br>
competitors; changes in law or the uncertainty of the application of law and regulation; the ability to attract and<br>
retain management and employees; the inability to successfully execute management strategies with respect to<br>
cost containment, production increases or decreases, inventory control, and the integration of acquired<br>
businesses, and general changes in economic and financial conditions, residential and non-residential<br>
construction and municipal spending.&#160; Risks associated with forward-looking statements are more fully described<br>
in our filings with the Securities and Exchange Commission. Aegean Marine Petroleum Network Inc. assumes no<br>
duty to update its forward-looking statements as of any future date.</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-TOP: 6px; LEFT: 55px; WIDTH: 936px; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.1399; POSITION: absolute; TOP: 471px; HEIGHT: 20px; TEXT-ALIGN: justify" nowrap><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: #094470; FONT-STYLE: italic; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; TEXT-DECORATION: underline">Non-GAAP Financial Measures</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-TOP: 6px; LEFT: 55px; WIDTH: 936px; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.1399; POSITION: absolute; TOP: 499px; HEIGHT: 84px; TEXT-ALIGN: justify" nowrap><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: #094470; FONT-STYLE: italic; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Within this presentation, the Company makes reference to certain non-GAAP financial measures, which have<br>
directly comparable GAAP financial measures as identified in this presentation. These non-GAAP measures are<br>
provided because they are used as standard metrics by the investment community. We believe these measures<br>
will assist the investment community in properly assessing the underlying performance of the Company.</font></div>

<div style="LEFT: 27px; WIDTH: 991px; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.2; POSITION: absolute; TOP: 61px; HEIGHT: 44px; TEXT-ALIGN: left" nowrap><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 28pt; COLOR: #094470; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Company:</font><font style="FONT-SIZE: 28pt; COLOR: #094470; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 21px">&#160;</font>Operations</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-TOP: 17px; LEFT: 39px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 12px; WIDTH: 917px; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.2; POSITION: absolute; TOP: 418px; HEIGHT: 25px; TEXT-ALIGN: left" nowrap><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 0px; MARGIN-LEFT: 14px; HEIGHT: 0px">&#160;</font><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 12px">&#160;</font><font style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; COLOR: #094470; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Superior financing terms on newbuild ships</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-TOP: 1px; LEFT: 39px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 5px; WIDTH: 917px; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.2; POSITION: absolute; TOP: 474px; HEIGHT: 22px; TEXT-ALIGN: left" nowrap><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 0px; MARGIN-LEFT: 52px; HEIGHT: 0px">&#160;</font><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 14px">&#160;</font><font style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: #094470; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Aegean Marine financed newbuilds with 80% debt / 20% equity</font></div>

<div style="LEFT: 39px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 5px; WIDTH: 917px; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.2; POSITION: absolute; TOP: 503px; HEIGHT: 22px; TEXT-ALIGN: left" nowrap><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 0px; MARGIN-LEFT: 52px; HEIGHT: 0px">&#160;</font><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 14px">&#160;</font><font style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: #094470; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Competitors required to provide significant equity contribution</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-TOP: 26px; LEFT: 50px; WIDTH: 955px; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.0799; POSITION: absolute; TOP: 628px; HEIGHT: 22px; TEXT-ALIGN: left" nowrap><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 0px; MARGIN-LEFT: 14px; HEIGHT: 0px">&#160;</font><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 25px">&#160;</font><font style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; COLOR: #094470; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Well positioned for long-term cash flow growth</font></div>

<div style="LEFT: 31px; WIDTH: 952px; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.2; POSITION: absolute; TOP: 123px; HEIGHT: 25px; TEXT-ALIGN: left" nowrap><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; COLOR: #094470; FONT-STYLE: italic; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Aegean Marine is a global marine fuel logistics company that markets and physically</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-TOP: 5px; LEFT: 31px; WIDTH: 952px; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.2; POSITION: absolute; TOP: 149px; HEIGHT: 24px; TEXT-ALIGN: left" nowrap><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; COLOR: #094470; FONT-STYLE: italic; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">supplies refined marine fuel and lubricants to ships in port and at sea&#8230;</font></div>
